“GoPro Take Photo” - I was humbled, stoked, and honoured the day @bri_adventures16 reached out wanting to film a short documentary about my passion for travel, the outdoors, and my journey shooting with @gopro. 📸 This camera and so many people in the #GoProFamily have added so much positivity to my life. I am constantly in awe of all the talent and continuously inspired by this community. Thankful to see all the creative lifestyles unfold and be able to call a lot of them my friends. 🤝🏼

Exploring the beauty of nature and being outside has always brought my soul happiness. I’ve driven thousands of kilometres in the SUV throughout these beautiful lands. It’s been such a thrill getting out on the open road throughout Canada and capturing it through the lens of #GoPro. This camera has changed my life and the way I see the world over the years. I’m so grateful to have their support along the way. 🙏🏼🤍 Here’s to creating more memories. Hope you enjoy the clips! 

Hats off and huge shoutout to Bri, @das_pics, and the rest of the crew for the opportunity and hard work bringing all of this to life. Appreciate you for telling more of my story behind the camera. 😀

Thanks for following along and supporting the journey. Peace and love. ☮️🍻 Stay adventurous! 🤟🏼 #Hero11 #GoProMax #ExploreCanada
